  What if the things in the night didn't just go bump? BlindSide is a
  terrifying new audio-only adventure game, set in a fully-immersive 3D world
  you'll never see. Put on your headphones, close your eyes, and explore the
  darkness. Listen as the world rotates around you!
 
  You play as Case, an assistant professor who wakes up blind, to find his
  city destroyed and mysterious creatures devouring people. Will you and your
  girlfriend be able to find your way without sight? How will you escape? Run
  for your life, navigate the darkness, and uncover the mystery of the
  apocalypse--all in the dark!
 
  BlindSide was inspired by co-creator Aaron Rasmussen's temporary blindness
  as a result of an explosion in high school chemistry.
 
  Features:
  ~~~~~~~~~
  - Over 1000 sound effects and pieces of dialogue
  - A new level of audio-based horror
  - Accessible for blind and sighted users alike
